            'zh-CN': "**技术原理**\n\n追焦(Panning)是跟随移动主体水平转动相机,同时使用较慢快门速度拍摄,创造主体清晰、背景模糊的动态效果:\n\n• **相机移动**:以与主体相同速度水平转动相机\n• **快门速度**:使用1/30s至1/125s的慢速快门\n• **动态模糊**:背景产生水平方向的运动模糊\n• **速度感**:视觉上强化主体的运动感和速度\n\n**实际应用场景**\n\n• 运动摄影:赛车、自行车、跑步选手\n• 野生动物:飞鸟、奔跑的动物\n• 街拍:行驶的车辆、骑车的人\n• 创意摄影:任何水平移动的主体\n\n**拍摄技巧与参数**\n\n• 快门速度:慢速主体1/30s,快速主体1/125s\n• 追踪技巧:保持主体在取景框相同位置\n• 身体姿势:以腰部为轴心旋转,保持上身稳定\n• 连拍模式:提高成功率,多拍几张选最佳\n• 对焦设定:使用连续自动对焦(AF-C)追踪主体\n\n**常见误区**\n\n✗ 误区:快门速度越慢效果越好\n✓ 正解:需平衡,过慢会使主体也模糊\n\n✗ 误区:只能拍摄快速移动的主体\n✓ 正解:慢速移动也可以,调整快门速度即可",
            'en': "**Technical Principles**\n\nPanning involves horizontally rotating the camera to follow a moving subject while using a slow shutter speed, creating a sharp subject against a blurred background:\n\n• **Camera Movement**: Rotate camera horizontally at same speed as subject\n• **Shutter Speed**: Use slow shutter 1/30s to 1/125s\n• **Motion Blur**: Background shows horizontal motion blur\n• **Speed Sensation**: Visually emphasizes subject's movement and velocity\n\n**Practical Applications**\n\n• Sports Photography: Racing cars, cyclists, runners\n• Wildlife: Flying birds, running animals\n• Street Photography: Moving vehicles, cyclists\n• Creative Photography: Any horizontally moving subject\n\n**Shooting Techniques & Settings**\n\n• Shutter Speed: Slow subjects 1/30s, fast subjects 1/125s\n• Tracking Technique: Keep subject in same position in viewfinder\n• Body Posture: Rotate from waist, keep upper body stable\n• Burst Mode: Increase success rate, shoot multiple frames\n• Focus Setting: Use continuous autofocus (AF-C) to track subject\n\n**Common Misconceptions**\n\n✗ Myth: Slower shutter speed always better\n✓ Truth: Need balance; too slow blurs subject too\n\n✗ Myth: Only works for fast-moving subjects\n✓ Truth: Works for slow movement too; adjust shutter speed",
